<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net">
  <diagram name="Página-1" id="v4w0xNLlb51hintJ34AH">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1664" dy="815" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml predict_inprocess_python\ntitle Predict — In-Process + Python Backend\n\nskinparam sequenceMessageAlign center\nskinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true\nskinparam maxMessageSize 200\nskinparam ParticipantPadding 20\nskinparam BoxPadding 10\nskinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5\nskinparam roundcorner 5\nskinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #333333\nskinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #333333\nskinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #DAE8FC\nskinparam sequenceActorBorderColor #333333\nskinparam noteBorderColor #AAAAAA\nskinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFFCC\n\nactor \&quot;Caller\&quot; as Caller\n\nbox \&quot;miia::client\&quot; #EAF4FB\n    participant \&quot;InferenceClient\&quot; as IC\n    participant \&quot;InProcessBackend\&quot; as IPB\nend box\n\nbox \&quot;miia::worker (in-process)\&quot; #EAF7EA\n    participant \&quot;InferenceEngine\&quot; as IE\n    participant \&quot;PythonBackend\&quot; as PB\nend box\n\nbox \&quot;CPython Interpreter (embedded)\&quot; #FFF8E7\n    participant \&quot;MiiaModel\\n(user .py)\&quot; as Model\nend box\n\nnote over IC, IPB\n  **Sem gRPC — sem serialização proto**\n  client::Object passado diretamente\n  target == \&quot;inprocess\&quot; | \&quot;in_process\&quot; | \&quot;local\&quot;\nend note\n\nnote over PB, Model\n  CPython embarcado no mesmo processo\n  GIL gerenciado via PyGILState_Ensure/Release\n  numpy C-API inicializada uma vez (flag estático)\nend note\n\n== Setup (já conectado) ==\n\nCaller -&gt; IC : predict(\\n  model_id : string,\\n  inputs : Object)\nactivate IC\n\nIC -&gt; IPB : predict(\\n  model_id : string,\\n  inputs : client::Object)\nactivate IPB\n\nIPB -&gt; IE : predict(\\n  model_id : string,\\n  inputs : client::Object\\n) : InferenceResult\nactivate IE\n\nnote right of IE\n  Lock mutex_\n  backend* = models_[model_id].backend.get()\n  Unlock mutex_\nend note\n\nIE -&gt; PB : predict(\\n  inputs : client::Object\\n) : InferenceResult\nactivate PB\n\nPB -&gt; PB : PyGILState_Ensure()\\n→ gstate : PyGILState_STATE\n\nPB -&gt; PB : inputs_to_py_dict(\\n  inputs : client::Object\\n) : PyObject* dict\n\nnote right of PB\n  Para cada (name, val) em inputs:\n    value_to_py(val) → PyObject*\n    recursivo para:\n      double  → PyFloat_FromDouble()\n      bool    → PyBool_FromLong()\n      string  → PyUnicode_FromString()\n      Array   → PyList_New() + SET_ITEM\n      Object  → PyDict_New() + SetItem\n    PyDict_SetItem(dict, key, py_val)\nend note\n\nPB -&gt; PB : PyTuple_Pack(1, py_inputs)\\n: PyObject* args\n\nPB -&gt; Model : PyObject_CallObject(\\n  py_predict_method_ : PyObject*,\\n  args : PyObject*\\n) : PyObject* py_result\nactivate Model\n\nnote right of Model\n  model.predict(inputs: dict)\n  Acessa inputs como dict Python\n  Processa com numpy/lógica própria\n  Retorna dict[str, np.ndarray]\nend note\n\nModel --&gt; PB : PyObject*\\n(dict[str, np.ndarray])\ndeactivate Model\n\nPB -&gt; PB : Py_DECREF(args)\\nPy_DECREF(py_inputs)\n\nPB -&gt; PB : py_dict_to_outputs(\\n  py_result : PyObject*,\\n  outputs : client::Object&amp;,\\n  error : string&amp;\\n) : bool\n\nnote right of PB\n  PyDict_Check(py_dict)\n  Para cada (key, value) via PyDict_Next():\n    PyUnicode_AsUTF8(key) → name\n    PyArray_FROMANY(value,\\n      NPY_FLOAT32,\\n      NPY_ARRAY_C_CONTIGUOUS\\n      | NPY_ARRAY_FORCECAST)\n    PyArray_SIZE()  → total : npy_intp\n    PyArray_DATA()  → ptr : float*\n    total == 1 → Value{double(ptr[0])}\n    total &gt;  1 → Value{Array{...}}\n  Py_DECREF(arr)\nend note\n\nPB -&gt; PB : Py_DECREF(py_result)\n\nPB -&gt; PB : PyGILState_Release(gstate)\n\nPB -&gt; PB : touch()\\nmetrics_.record(time_ms, true)\n\nPB --&gt; IE : InferenceResult {\\n  success: true,\\n  outputs: client::Object,\\n  inference_time_ms: double\\n}\ndeactivate PB\n\nIE --&gt; IPB : InferenceResult\ndeactivate IE\n\nIPB -&gt; IPB : result.success           = r.success\\nresult.inference_time_ms = r.inference_time_ms\\nresult.outputs           = move(r.outputs)\n\nIPB --&gt; IC : PredictionResult {\\n  success: bool,\\n  outputs: client::Object,\\n  inference_time_ms: double\\n}\ndeactivate IPB\n\nIC --&gt; Caller : PredictionResult\ndeactivate IC\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="OFugE89OlIWmUVSY5UGE-5">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="1975" width="1524" x="20" y="1132" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
